Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.96,0:07:57.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想守住这个约定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.30,0:08:55.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑同学 也承受着这样的疼痛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.16,0:08:58.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.19,0:09:05.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么启动了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.34,0:09:07.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羽佐间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.91,0:09:09.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁在驾驶Mk.Ⅵ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.79,0:09:11.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羽佐间！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.81,0:09:16.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 让Mk.Ⅵ出击？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.64,0:09:19.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了 快阻止翔子 皆城
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.50,0:09:23.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆城！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.12,0:09:26.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.17,0:09:29.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护龙宫岛 是我们的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.63,0:09:35.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 羽佐间翔子是最适合驾驶Mk.Ⅵ的人选
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.34,0:09:39.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一点您应该知道吧 羽佐间老师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.62,0:09:41.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这 这…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.59,0:09:46.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备出击了 羽佐间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.23,0:09:49.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 皆城同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.76,0:10:09.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Ⅵ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.10,0:10:12.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驾驶员是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.93,0:10:17.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难不成…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.15,0:10:23.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 真的…是翔子吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.68,0:10:39.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小楯你看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.08,0:10:41.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,输出平衡不对头
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.13,0:10:47.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让Mk.Ⅵ先回来 举升发动机需要重新调整
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.13,0:10:47.01,ruby,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(748,1000)}lift engine
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.53,0:10:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 真壁！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.99,0:10:52.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有必要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.30,0:10:54.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要声张
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.35,0:10:57.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别命令大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.04,0:11:13.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Alvis内部受损范围扩大到B4-86区
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.08,0:11:17.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Ⅵ 从上空接近
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.56,0:11:18.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.80,0:11:24.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.89,0:11:37.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.66,0:11:42.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在那里吗
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(Part-b)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.64,0:12:34.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这招…怎么样！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.35,0:12:54.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.52,0:12:55.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑 马上回岛去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.18,0:12:57.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Alvis有危险
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.39,0:13:10.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是API-1的法芙娜的力量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.62,0:13:40.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从一骑同学的岛上滚出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.41,0:13:46.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羽佐间 短刀是打不倒它的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.41,0:13:46.62,ruby,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(646,1000)}Mind Blade
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.02,0:14:13.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脑波出现紊乱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.13,0:14:14.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.78,0:14:17.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Ⅵ打不倒它吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.30,0:14:46.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的 羽佐间 羽佐间！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.62,0:15:23.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.31,0:15:27.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样把它拖出岛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.40,0:15:44.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 在上空让诺伦攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.75,0:16:02.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以了 放开质问者型
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.80,0:16:06.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 羽佐间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.45,0:16:08.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我放不开
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.39,0:16:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.99,0:16:19.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快脱离 羽佐间！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.58,0:16:26.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆城同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.12,0:16:30.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要使用芬里尔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.12,0:16:30.65,ruby,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(830,1000)}Fenrir
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.12,0:16:30.65,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,注：名称来源于北欧神话中的巨狼芬里尔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.21,0:16:32.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,代码已认证
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.88,0:16:34.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芬里尔 启动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.36,0:16:39.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羽佐间…！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.15,0:16:42.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芬里尔 解除代码无法访问
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.86,0:16:43.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.07,0:16:48.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会保护你的岛的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.25,0:16:57.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子怎么会…！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.77,0:17:01.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.42,0:17:07.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总士 到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.42,0:17:10.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别干傻事！翔子！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.84,0:17:26.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆城
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.43,0:17:29.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把翔子还给我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.74,0:17:32.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甲洋！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.14,0:17:32.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春日井！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.42,0:17:36.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驾驶员候补都给我待命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.92,0:17:38.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不准擅离职守
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.19,0:17:43.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你们几个！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.35,0:17:44.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.74,0:17:46.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真矢！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.12,0:18:01.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.62,0:18:33.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芬里尔爆炸级别 设定为最大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.91,0:18:37.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羽佐间…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.91,0:18:48.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子——！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.08,0:18:53.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.47,0:19:04.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.53,0:19:07.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 是妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.53,0:19:08.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是妈妈哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.58,0:19:10.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.53,0:19:13.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戴上看看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.27,0:19:24.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 我为什么叫翔子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.54,0:19:25.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.72,0:19:28.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈希望你能在高高的天上翱翔呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.54,0:19:29.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翱翔？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.10,0:19:32.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是在天上飞的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.78,0:19:35.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这片天上翱翔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.43,0:19:39.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.11,0:19:47.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正 我又不是你的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.74,0:19:53.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 说了那种话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.66,0:19:56.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.82,0:20:06.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不是遵守约定了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.49,0:20:09.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.47,0:20:43.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么…样了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.29,0:20:51.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Ⅵ 和Festum一起…消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.18,0:21:18.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.04,0:21:20.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是真的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.02,0:21:22.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.40,0:21:26.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.69,0:21:31.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和贵重的Mk.Ⅵ一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.94,0:21:34.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.65,0:21:45.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抬头看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.65,0:21:50.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一天 那个晴空万里的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.15,0:21:52.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却下起了雨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.21,0:21:57.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 她却微笑着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.41,0:22:03.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向被淋得湿透的我们递出了伞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.41,0:22:06.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.60,0:22:09.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「天空啊 请不要哭泣」
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（ED-v2）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.98,0:23:23.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少女在空中消散
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.64,0:23:26.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少年急于战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.63,0:23:29.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大人面露愠色
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.29,0:23:34.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却也是他们泣不成声
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.09,0:23:39.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子们唯有淋湿在绝望的雨中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.24,0:23:44.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 苍穹的法芙娜 第七回
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.87,0:23:45.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家贼 -亲子-
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.16,0:23:49.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在那里吗
